import React,{useState} from 'react' import { useNavigate,Link } from 'react-router-dom' import "../styles/Register.css"; import Alert from './Alert'; const Register = () => { let navigate = useNavigate(); const [credentials, setCredentials] = useState({"email":"","password":"","cpassword":"","countrycode":"countrycode","mobilenumber":"","firstname":"", "lastname":"","dateofbirth":"","gender":"","nationality":"India"}) const [placeholder, setPlaceholder] = useState({"fname":"dnone","lname":"dnone","email":"dnone", "pwd":"dnone","cpwd":"dnone","mobilenumber":"dnone"}) const [height,setHeight] = useState({"fname":"ihide", "lname":"ihide","email":"ihide", "pwd":"ihide","cpwd":"ihide","mobilenumber":"ihide"}) const [alert,setAlert] = useState({}) const [alertborder, setAlertborder] = useState({"email":"","password":"","cpassword":"","countrycode":"","mobilenumber":"","firstname":"", "lastname":"","dateofbirth":"","gender":"","nationality":""}) const onChangelogin = (e) => { setCredentials({...credentials,[e.target.name]:e.target.value}) } const handleSubmit = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); const response = await fetch ("http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth",{ method:'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: JSON.stringify({email: credentials.email, password: credentials.password, countrycode: credentials.countrycode, mobilenumber: credentials.mobilenumber, firstname: credentials.firstname, lastname: credentials.lastname, dateofbirth: credentials.dateofbirth, gender:credentials.gender, nationality: credentials.nationality }) }) const json = await response.json() if (json.success){ // Save the auth token and redirect localStorage.setItem('token', json.authtoken); navigate('/'); } else{ alert('try again') } } const setNationlity = (e) => { setCredentials({...credentials,"nationality":e.target.getAttribute('data-value')}) } const setCountrycode = (e) => { setCredentials({...credentials,"countrycode":e.target.getAttribute('data-value')}) } return (
